snippet.title: The Charnel House Trilogy [1]
snippet.description:
Charnel House Trilogy: http://store.steampowered.com/app/288930/ ($6)
Charnel House Trilogy Playlist: http://bit.ly/hccharnelhousetrilogy
This is a point-and-click horror adventure game made by Owl Cave - you may remember that I played "Sepulchre" a while back! Hope you guys enjoy, and thanks for watching!

PLAYLISTS - http://bit.ly/HCPlaylists

Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/HarshlyCritical
Twitter - https://twitter.com/harshlycritical
Upload schedule - http://www.harshlycritical.com

Outro art by - oweeo - http://oweeo.deviantart.com/

Outro music by - Artificial Construct - http://on.fb.me/1wedGnL

Channel avatar by - Kat Wynn - http://on.fb.me/1qAnRja
